snippet.title: Truth few people know about Amber Heard
snippet.description:

Heard was born in Austin, Texas, to Patricia Paige (née Parsons), an internet researcher (1956–2020), and David Clinton Heard (born 1950), who owned a small construction company.She has a younger sister, Whitney. The family lived outside Austin.
Thank you all for watching the video.
